    "course_title": "ANATOMY OF THE LARGE DOMESTIC ANIMALS",
    "description": "A study of the horse and the ox with special emphasis on the anatomical specializations of these species with extensive comparisons to the anatomy of the small domestic animals. Other large domestic animals, including swine, will be considered as appropriate to demonstrate anatomical variation.",
